Source: @PACKAGE_NAME@
Section: interpreters
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Docker Hardened Images <dhi@docker.com>
Homepage: https://www.ruby-lang.org/
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13)
Standards-Version: 4.7.0

Package: @PACKAGE_NAME@
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, ca-certificates, libyaml-0-2, libjemalloc2
Provides: ruby (= ${binary:Version})
Conflicts: ruby, ruby-3.3, ruby-3.4, ruby-4.0
Replaces: ruby
Description: Ruby @MAJOR_MINOR@ interpreter
 Ruby is an interpreted object-oriented scripting language. This package
 provides the Ruby @MAJOR_MINOR@.x release line built with YJIT and jemalloc.

Package: @PACKAGE_NAME@-dev
Architecture: any
Depends: @PACKAGE_NAME@ (= ${binary:Version}), ${misc:Depends}
Provides: ruby-dev
Conflicts: ruby-dev, ruby-3.3-dev, ruby-3.4-dev, ruby-4.0-dev
Replaces: ruby-dev
Description: Ruby @MAJOR_MINOR@ development tools and headers
 Development headers, gem tooling, and auxiliary Ruby commands for the
 @PACKAGE_NAME@ package.
